Description: Fix hardcoded CXX flags in Makefile
 The upstream Makefile hardcodes CXX=g++ with specific flags. Strip them
 so the build uses the system default compiler and flags.
Author: pistomp <pistomp@example.com>
Forwarded: not-needed
Last-Update: 2026-06-22

--- a/Makefile
+++ b/Makefile
@@ -1,4 +1,4 @@
-CXX=g++ -O2 -std=c++11 -g -Wno-write-strings
+CXX=g++
 
 all: amidithru
```

